content:
Life Sciences Cloud Has New Objects

Store and access more data with these new Life Sciences Cloud objects.

Participant Management

* Represent the details of a research study that includes its design, execution, and oversight. Use the new ResearchStudy object.
* Represent the details of the research participant, which includes the associated account and the status of the subject. Use the new ResearchStudyCandidate object.
* ...
 
Care Program Management
Specify the status code for scheduling a service appointment group. Use the new CurrentEnrolleeCount field in the CareProgram object.

Electronic Signatures

* Specify the user or user group who can provide verification for a parent reference record. Use the new DesignatedVerifier field in the DigitalVerification object.
 
Adverse Events
Represent the event related to unintended/anticipated effects on research participants. Use the new AdverseEventEntry object.
title: Life Sciences Cloud Object Updates
